    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but \"sparks\" and \"kindness\" don't change the fact that the universe is just indifferent. it’s all just physics and decay. honestly, it feels more like a relief to just accept that there's nothing there instead of trying to fight it.",
      "source": "evaluator"
    },
